config BR2_PACKAGE_BREAKPAD
	bool "breakpad"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_GYP
	select BR2_PACKAGE_GTEST
	select BR2_PACKAGE_PROTOBUF
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LSS
	help
	  Breakpad is a library and tool suite that allows you to distribute
	  an application to users with compiler-provided debuuging information
	  removed, record crashes in compact \"minidump\" files, send them back
	  to your server, and produce C and C++ stack traces from these minidumps.
	  https://bugs.chromium.org/p/google-breakpad
